     <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">
      <h2 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name">他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！</h2>
      <div class="rich_media_meta_list">
       <em id="post-date" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">2016-08-12</em> 
       <!----> 
       <em id="post-date" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">素食惠</em> 
       <!-- --> 
       <a class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_link rich_media_meta_nickname" href="http://www.jiuchisu.com/m/list/fid/509" id="post-user">素食惠</a>
       <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text rich_media_meta_nickname">素食惠</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rich_media_content " id="js_content">
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">一个人，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">37年，5500000平方米，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他说：或许我贫穷吧，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">可我拥有了一整片森林。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">森林之子</strong></span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Forest Man</p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Majul，是印度最荒凉的地方，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">炎热的气候，干旱的沙漠，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">仿佛是无人可以居住的火星。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">远处一个老人的背影出现在远方，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">看起来他像是这个世界最后的居民，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">光着脚，在土地上留下一串脚印。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_lnxgt__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">跟着他走了不远，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">一座森林突然出现在了眼前。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这些树，全是他一个人种出来的，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">整整花了37年。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_cwk2u__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">“37年前，这里可不是这样的。”</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav Payeng的讲述，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">把你带回了他16岁那年的夏天。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_9me4n__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">故事要追溯到1979年，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">在连续几场灾难性的洪水过后，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">树木连同家园都被冲刷得一干二净，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">16岁的Jadav看到贫瘠的沙地上</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">躺着大片大片干瘪的死蛇。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_xuwkw__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_dykbo__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他被眼前的场景所震惊，问长辈们</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">我们会不会有一天也像这些蛇一样死去？</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">然而大家只是嘲笑他，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他却暗自下定决心要让这片荒地变得更绿一些。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_awpga__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他给政府写信，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">得到的只是讽刺的答复，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">让他自己去种树。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">然而他真的去种了，</strong><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></span></strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">而且这一种就是37年。</strong><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_4qust__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">从长辈那得到一些建议和竹子的种子后，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他便开始认真地在沙地上丈量、</span><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">挖坑、埋种、浇水。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_e3mjf__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">为了更方便种树，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他把家安在布拉马普特拉河岸边的小岛上，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">一家五口就生活在一间用木头搭起的小屋子里。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_waamd__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">每天凌晨4点不到，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">就要爬起来挤牛奶，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">因为要赶在八点前送到隔壁镇上去，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这是他们一家唯一的经济来源，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">被用来贴补家用，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">也用来购买树苗和工具。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_hkgvg__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">完成家中的劳务后</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他就拎上水桶、拿把镰刀，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">到家附近的沙地种一些树苗，直到深夜。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_oqyxd__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">随着树林面积越来越大，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">浇水成为了最头疼的事情。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他无法仅凭一己之力，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">每天将河边的水引流到所有的树苗。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_cuglq__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">于是他发明了竹子浇水系统，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">每株树苗上设有一根竹子轨道，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">上面放着有一些孔洞的土盆，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">水可以顺着竹子滴到树苗上，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">一盆水可以用上一两周。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_mnzh6__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav还引入白蚁、蚂蚁、蚯蚓和一些其它昆虫来改善土壤的条件。<strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">“昆虫们很擅于提升泥土的肥沃程度，它们在坚硬的石头表面钻来钻去，能够<strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">疏松</strong>土壤，更易于开垦，比机器更高效。”</strong>他说。</span><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_xuwkw__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">几十年种树如一日，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">在Jadav的不懈坚持下，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">树林变得越发茂密，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">甚至引来了许多大型的野生动物，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">第一次听见大象的吼叫时，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他兴奋地跑回家迫不及待地告诉妻儿。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_1w5r7__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">但同时，这也给周围的村民造成了极大的困扰：大象跑到农田里偷吃庄稼，破坏农作物，老虎在村子里捕食野鸡野鸟。</span><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">愤怒的村民们跑到Jadav家中闹事，殴打他，甚至威胁他说要砍掉他的森林，即便如此Jadav仍不放弃。</strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_ngco9__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav说，只要森林里有足够的食物，它们就不会跑到村里扰乱人们的生活了。他开始种更多更多的树，尤其是那些动物们可以取食的果树，比如大象爱吃的香蕉。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_8ofdd__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">渐渐地，森林里的物种越发丰富，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">鹿群逐渐增大，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">孟加拉虎、印度犀牛、兔子都来了。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这儿还是许多鸟类的家，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">甚至还有秃鹰，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">每年都会有约100头的象</span><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">群</span><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">迁徙至此</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">居住长达6个月之久。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_iknrm__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_ny9ff__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_awpga__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">从寸草不生的荒芜之地，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">到枝繁叶茂的热带雨林，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav一直是一个人在种树，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">村民们常排挤他，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">连朋友也质疑他。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">唯有家人一直无条件支持他，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他们一家五口在森林边搭建了草屋，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如果需要种更多的树，</strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">妻子和儿女们也会帮忙。</strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_tnzfr__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2012年，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav被印度尼赫鲁大学环境科学学院</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">授予<strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">“印度森林之子”</strong>的荣誉；</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2013年，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">来自加拿大、美国、印度等国家的电影制作者</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">纷纷将他的事迹拍成纪录片，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">比如<strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">《Forest Man》</strong>,</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">以鼓舞更多的人保护自然；</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2015年，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他被授予印度第四大最高平民奖项</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Padma Shree奖</strong><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">……</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_ny9ff__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_bdshq__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav从小就是个成绩优异的孩子，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他曾立志成为一名工程师，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">却因为种树牺牲了自己最初的梦想，</strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">但他从未后悔过。</strong></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">“儿时一起念书的好友，有五个都成为了工程师，搬到城市里住进了舒适的公寓，而我却牺牲了所有的东西，坚守这片土地，这片丛林就是我的家。我获得的认可和奖项就是对我的财富，我是世界上最幸福的人。“</strong><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他说。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_kmjqk__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如今这片550万平方米的丛林，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">被人们称为<strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">MOLAI FOREST</strong>，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">是以Jadav的小名命名的。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Jadav认为，现在的教育模式应该改变，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">每个孩子应该被要求每天种两棵树，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">而不是只会学习。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_qilie__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">已经拥有550万平方米森林的Jadav，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">有了大片的丰富绿洲，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">有了很多的荣誉，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他仍未停止前行。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">现在的他又投身到邻近的</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">150万平方米的沙地绿化工作中去了。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他要一直一直不停种树，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">直到和树木融为一体的那一天。</strong><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_bakvg__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">一个平凡的大叔，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">自己一个人花了37年的时间，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">种出了一片比纽约中央公园还要大的森林。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">他正企图用自己的力量，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">让这个已经伤痕累累的地球，变得好一点点。</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="他独自一人用37年，在荒漠上亲手种出550万平方米的森林，震惊世界！" src="http://www.jiuchisu.com/upload_files/article/509/199_uh0dp__.jpg" /></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">“这世界不是你们能改变的，</span></p>
       <p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">还是改变自己的想法吧。 ”</span></p>
